POLICY -- PANAMA; USSR -- FOREIGN POLICY -- LATIN AMERICA; PANAMA -- 
GOVERNMENT; PANAMA -- REVOLTS; AMERICANS -- PANAMA; EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES; BUSH, 
