ANGELES TIMES; PUBLIC ACCESS; PRIVACY; FINN, JIMMIE J; EMPLOYEE THEFTS; 
ROBBERIES -- LOS ANGELES; LOS ANGELES POLICE COMMISSION; POLICE -- LOS ANGELES 
