ANGELES COUNTY BOARD OF SUPERVISORS; DANA, DEANE; UNITED STATES -- SUITS; 
RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; REAPPORTIONMENT -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; POLITICAL 
CAMPAIGNS; HISPANICS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; REPUBLICAN PARTY (CALIFORNIA) 
</P>
