<TEXT>
<P>
Wattson Charter Buildings in Irvine will consist of two four-story office 
buildings and a four-level parking structure. The project is located on a 
259,000-square-foot parcel of land and will contain more than 192,000 square 
feet of office space. Ground-breaking is scheduled for September, 1990, with 
completion expected in October. 
