Hoffman in 1973, after being freed from the "Hanoi Hilton" POW camp where he 
had been held for 15 months. ; Photo, COLOR, Dave Rehmann with the Corvette 
given to him when he was freed from a North Vietnamese prison in 1973 after 
more than 6 1/2 years as a POW.; Photo, Right, Rehmann after he was shot down 
over North Vietnam; suffering severe burns and a broken arm. DAVID MURONAKA / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
